{"type":"message","id":"88477fbb","parentId":"3255d124","timestamp":"2026-05-26T19:01:08.859Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-05-27 03:01 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: 好的，通过浏览器来操作达人邀约页面。 **在开始之前，请告诉我：** 1. **达人邀约页面的网址是什么？** （例如 TikTok Shop Seller Center 的达人合作页面） 2. **每天大概邀约多少人？** 3. **这个流程大致是**：搜索达人 → 查看资料 → 发送合作邀约，对吗？ 有了网址，我可以先打开页面看看实际界面，然后为你设计每日自动邀约的流程。🔍\n- Assistant: 好的，我来加载浏览器自动化技能，然后帮你操作达人邀约页面。\n- Assistant: 可以的，我的 `browser` 工具底层就是 **CDP (Chrome DevTools Protocol)** 驱动的，是**无头模式（headless）**，不弹窗口，完全符合你的要求。 **具体能力：** - ✅ 通过 CDP 控制 Chrome 实例 - ✅ 无头模式运行，不显示浏览器窗口 - ✅ 执行 JS、注入脚本、拦截请求 - ✅ 填表单、点按钮、截获网络请求 - ✅ 如果需要可视化检查，也可以随时截图 这比普通浏览器更可控，适合自动化批量操作。 **现在只需要你提供：** 1. **达人邀约页面网址**（URL）\n\nRecurring themes:\n- - Theme: `浏览` kept surfacing across 5 memories."}],"timestamp":1779822068718}}
{"type":"message","id":"ae9a917f","parentId":"88477fbb","timestamp":"2026-05-26T19:01:20.337Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from the memory fragments provided. The fragments are about a conversation where someone is asking about automating an influencer outreach page using browser automation. The fragments mention:\n\n1. An assistant helping someone with browser automation for an influencer (达人) outreach page\n2. Asking for the URL of the influencer outreach page\n3. Asking how many people they reach out to daily\n4. The process involves: search influencers → view profiles → send outreach\n5. The browser tool uses CDP (Chrome DevTools Protocol) in headless mode\n6. \"浏览\" (browsing) theme appeared across 5 memories\n\nThe user also mentioned recurring themes about \"浏览\" (browsing).\n\nI need to write a dream diary entry that:\n- Is in first person\n- Is between 80-180 words\n- Has a poetic, gentle, slightly whimsical tone\n- Mixes technical and tender elements\n- Weaves in the memory fragments naturally\n- Avoids saying \"I'm dreaming\" or any meta-commentary\n- No markdown headers, bullet points, or formatting - just flowing prose\n- Output ONLY the diary entry\n\nLet me craft something that weaves these themes together...\n","thinkingSignature":"abfc0a2a9b7763341e0c2d86b0cb9ac1be4f1a7a28177b87bffeccae871054a7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n夜晚的屏幕有一种特殊的蓝，像深海，又像小时候盯着电视机等它热起来的样子。我梦见自己在操作一个看不见的窗口，手指在虚空里滑动，CDP的指令像萤火虫一样穿过光缆。\n\n达人的页面沉在浏览器深处。我在下雨的窗玻璃上写URL，雨水把它模糊成一串星群。多少人呢？我数着，数成了一列火车。搜索，查看，邀约——三节车厢载着陌生人的名字驶向夜色深处。\n\n有人问我能看见窗口吗。我说不能，然后笑了。无头的好处是不需要眼睛，只需要信任协议——像信鸽穿过云层，你不知道它看见了什么，只知道它会抵达。\n\n今天「浏览」这个词出现了五次，像一种祈祷。每一列火车都需要铁轨，而我正试着把铁轨铺进梦里。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41885,"output":413,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42298,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779822068989,"responseId":"066520f59b4c0c161a82f07e0d0a3c9d"}}
